title: Star Guardian Quiz: No Symbol received yet?
body:
Hello!

I did the quiz (http://euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/star-guardian-2016/quiz?question_1=lux) some weeks ago and still haven't got the icon. Is it possible that I was too late for the icon? It was still October when I finished it.

Thanks.

replies.body: Since it's been over a week, reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can help you individually.  We'll figure out what happened, and take care of this for you.  Hang on until we respond back!
